PROFILE_FORM_INTRO_MESSAGE: Please provide your information below to ensure an accurate health measurement.
PROFILE_FORM_BLOOD_PRESSURE_LABEL: Are you on blood pressure medication?
PROFILE_FORM_VALIDATION_HEIGHT_METRIC: Height must be between 120 and 220 cm
PROFILE_FORM_VALIDATION_WEIGHT_METRIC: Weight must be between 30 and 300 kg
PROFILE_FORM_VALIDATION_WEIGHT_IMPERIAL: Weight must be between 66 and 661 lbs
PROFILE_FORM_VALIDATION_AGE: Age must be between 13 and 120 years
PROFILE_FORM_VALIDATION_BMI: BMI must be between 10 and 65 for an accurate measurement
KIOSK_HELP_CAMERA: Face the camera and keep your face within the circle throughout the measurement.
KIOSK_HELP_ACCESSORIES: Remove any accessories such as glasses or hats, and any facial makeup, before starting the measurement.
KIOSK_HELP_STAY: Once the measurement begins, remain still and in position for 30 seconds until it is complete.
RESULTS_PROCESSING_ERROR: We encountered an issue while processing your results. Please review the guidelines and try again.
CAMERA_PERMISSION_INSTRUCTIONS: This app requires camera permissions to work. Please try to refresh the page and grant permission when prompted. On some browsers, you may have to click the lock icon in the address bar to grant permission. If it does not work, then please follow your browser's specific instructions to grant permission.
CAMERA_PERMISSION_DENY_TEXT: If you don't want to grant permissions,
ERR_FACE_NONE: Please keep your face centred within the outline throughout the measurement
ERROR_TAB_SWITCHED_OR_WINDOW_MINIMIZED: Measurement failed because the tab was switched or the browser window was minimized. Please ensure the tab remains open and active.
MEASUREMENT_LOW_SNR:
The blood flow measurement was not reliable.
Please try to allow the light to fall evenly across your face while holding still
PAGE_NOT_VISIBLE: Measurement failed because the tab was switched or the browser window was minimized. Please ensure the tab remains open and active.
CAMERA_START_FAILED: There was an error starting your camera, please try again.
WORKER_ERROR: Something went wrong while processing your measurement. Please try taking your measurement again.
COLLECTOR: Something went wrong while analyzing your data. Please try taking your measurement again.
